cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.IR. 

The paper proposes a method based on convolutional neural networks for semi-automatic labeling of RECIST annotations on CT scans. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could place it in cs.MED (Medical Imaging) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
